== 制作 ==
该片得到[[NBA|美国职业篮球协会]]授权和其旗下篮球明星加盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2012-05-31/22353645802.shtml|title=《神奇》预告黄晓明金雅中激情戏曝光|date=2012-05-31|accessdate=2014-03-16|work=新浪|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603132846/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2012-05-31/22353645802.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20130902/017502.htm |title=《神奇》曝终极海报 国庆假期High爆全城 |date=2013-09-02 |accessdate=2014-03-16 |work=腾讯网 |archive-date=2019-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613013325/https://ent.qq.com/a/20130902/017502.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://roll.sohu.com/20130927/n387337151.shtml |title=强手如林，《神奇》抢滩 |accessdate=2014-03-16 |date=2013-09-27 |work=搜狐 |archive-date=2019-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603132845/http://roll.sohu.com/20130927/n387337151.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>这也是美国职业篮球协会首次和中国大陆影视界合作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/13/1001/09/9A3G353D000300B1.html |title=黄晓明主演《神奇》 NBA首次与中国电影合作 |date=2013-10-01 |accessdate=2014-03-16 |work=网易 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608025426/http://ent.163.com/13/1001/09/9A3G353D000300B1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

